      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "STICKER PREP PIPELINE\n\nTurns any image into a print/sticker-ready transparent PNG: trims the\ntransparent border, adds a white sticker-cut outline, a soft drop\nshadow, then resizes onto a clean square canvas.\n\nFlow: Load Image -> Mask Adapter -> Trim -> Outline -> Drop Shadow ->\nResize Canvas -> Mask Adapter -> Join Image With Alpha -> Save Image.\n\nSet before running:\n  - Load Image: pick your own asset (needs a transparent background)\n  - Outline / Drop Shadow: colors and sizes to taste\n  - Resize Canvas: final width/height for your sticker\n\nThe two Mask Adapter nodes exist because ComfyUI's own LoadImage and\nJoinImageWithAlpha use the OPPOSITE mask convention from this package's\nnodes -- see the README's \"Core Concept: the Alpha Convention\" section."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "title": "README"
    },
